```

### 11. Sales Log (`wp_fn_sales_log`)
```json
{
    "number_id": 505,
    "dealer_id": 5,
    "buyer_id": 10,
    "order_id": 1,
    "sold_price": "50000.00"
}
```

### 12. WhatsApp Log (`wp_fn_whatsapp_log`)
```json
{
    "number_id": 505,
